Open data studio Jupyter is a fully managed machine learning (ML) notebook environment. It gives every developer and data scientist the ability to build, train models quickly. It integrates with other projects, such as [mlflow-server](https://staroid.com/g/open-datastudio/mlflow-server), to manage and deploy models.
:::

:::: section column
# Benefits

::: col 30%
## Fully managed
Click to deploy Jupyter instances to the cloud and region you like.
:::

::: col 30%
## Fork and Customize
[Fork](https://github.com/open-datastudio/jupyter) and customize to have your own version of a fully managed Jupyter environment for your team.
:::

::: col 30%
## GPU
Just select a GPU instance when launch.
Full GPU stack, from driver to machine learning framework, will be configured automatically.
:::
::::

:::: section
# For your teams and projects
Create [Virtualized Kubernetes clusters](https://staroid.com/site/why_staroid/kubernetes) per your team or per project. And manage, share your Jupyter instances in each cluster.
